text: Nathan Katz (born 17 January 1995) is an Australian judoka. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the men's 66 kg event, in which he was eliminated in the second round by Imad Bassou. His younger brother Josh Katz also competed for Australia in judo at the Rio Olympics. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Australian male judoka Category:Olympic judoka of Australia Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics
